  _recollection: {fileID: 0}
  _lines:
  - I'm sitting in my bedroom.
  - I'm watching some video on my computer. Uh, I think it was the music video for
    "My First Enemy" by Age of Madness
  - My headphones are on full blast, but I can still hear the yelling outside my
    door.
  - Something's thrown down the hall. Or maybe down the stairs.
  - 'I try not to listen. '
  _playerReplyOptions:
  - I look down at my hands
  - I look at my reflection in the screen.
  - I close my eyes.
